# Ignore everything in this directory by default — HA writes a LOT of
# runtime state here (database, .storage, logs, secrets) and we don't
# want any of it in git.
*

# Whitelist what we DO want tracked: hand-edited config YAMLs + docs +
# this gitignore itself.
!.gitignore
!configuration.yaml
!automations.yaml
!scripts.yaml
!scenes.yaml
!NOTES.md
